   <narrative xml:lang="EN">LIN&apos;s Covid-19 Emergency Community Fund 2021</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The 4th wave of Covid-19 pandemic has been back and hit drastically and directly Vietnamese community. This time around, it affects not only grassroots organizations but also the most vulnerable part of community - the poverty sector living with fluctuated daily income. There are several NPOs struggling to provide daily essentials to those who lost their income. LIN&apos;s Covid-19 Emergency Community Fund aims to give a hand to prolong these meaningful projects, right now and post-pandemic.</narrative>
  </description>
